---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SectionHeading from "../components/SectionHeading.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Organization - FIB"
  description="A clean overview of the FIB structure and how divisions fit together."
>
  <SectionHeading
    eyebrow="Organization"
    title="Divisions and support structure"
    description="A placeholder structure page designed for easy updates as you provide division details."
  />

  <div class="prose-fib max-w-3xl">
    <p>
      This page is for your public-facing overview of FIB organization. You can
      add an executive summary, a high-level diagram, or a short explanation
      of how the divisions work together.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4">
      Since this site is informational, the layout is intentionally kept
      simple and readable, with a focus on clear hierarchy.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

